data.description: 🌿 This charming retreat nestled in the cozy Riverside area! 🌊🏡 If you're searching for a cute and affordable house with a touch of serenity, then look no further - I've got just the place for you! This adorable 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom house is the epitome of comfort and simplicity, offering a tranquil oasis in a bustling world. With the added bonus of not one, but two sheds, this property is perfect for those seeking a minimalist lifestyle without compromising on storage space. Let's dive into all the wonderful features this little gem has to offer! ✨
